 注册\" style=\"outline:0px;border:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto 10px;max-width:600px;clear:both;\" />SHOPBOP 如何 注册</span>进入登录页面（无论点击登陆还是注册，都是进入下图的页面）。若已经有Amazon账户，则可点击“<strong style=\"outline:0px;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;color:#bb0200;\">Login with Amazon</span></strong>”；若没有Amazon账户，或想注册一个新账号，则可点击左下角“<strong style=\"outline:0px;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;color:#bb0200;\">请注册</span></strong>”，即可进入注册页面。</p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\"><span class=\"img_desc\" style=\"outline:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto;text-align:center;\"><img itemprop=\"image\" src=\"http://p.zdmimg.com/201410/10/5437bedb339ec.png_v6.jpg\" _size=\"16691\" alt=\"用Amazon 亚马逊账户登陆\" style=\"outline:0px;border:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto 10px;max-width:600px;clear:both;\" />用Amazon 亚马逊账户登陆</span></p><h3 style=\"outline:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;;color:#333333;line-height:26px;\">1.使用Amazon账户登陆</h3><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\">①若你之前用这个浏览器登陆过Amazon，则SHOPBOP会根据cookie纪录，自动识别你的Amazon账户；若确定选择使用此账户，则点“<strong style=\"outline:0px;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;color:#bb0200;\">Okay</span></strong>”即可进入完善注册步骤的页面；<br style=\"outline:0px;\" /></p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\"><span class=\"img_desc\" style=\"outline:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto;text-align:center;\"><img itemprop=\"image\" src=\"http://p.zdmimg.com/201410/10/5437bedc4e343.png_v6.jpg\" _size=\"26731\" alt=\"确认登录\" style=\"outline:0px;border:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto 10px;max-width:600px;clear:both;\" />确认登录</span></p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\">②若该账户不是你的Amazon用户，则可点击右上角的“<strong style=\"outline:0px;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;color:#bb0200;\">Not ***</span></strong>”，重新输入你的账户信息，如下图：</p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\"><span class=\"img_desc\" style=\"outline:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto;text-align:center;\"><img itemprop=\"image\" src=\"http://p.zdmimg.com/201410/10/5437bedce40c1.png_v6.jpg\" _size=\"18133\" alt=\"切换登录账户\" style=\"outline:0px;border:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto 10px;max-width:600px;clear:both;\" />切换登录账户</span>③通过Amazon账户登陆后，进入完善注册信息页面，当然这些信息在个人账户里的“<strong style=\"outline:0px;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;color:#bb0200;\">首选项</span></strong>”里，可以修改，并不是一次选定的。</p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\"><span class=\"img_desc\" style=\"outline:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto;text-align:center;\"><img itemprop=\"image\" src=\"http://p.zdmimg.com/201410/10/5437bede1049a.png_v6.jpg\" _size=\"19480\" alt=\"填写个人信息\" style=\"outline:0px;border:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto 10px;max-width:600px;clear:both;\" />填写个人信息</span></p><h3 style=\"outline:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;;color:#333333;line-height:26px;\">2.注册新账号</h3><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\">页面具备全中文提示，大家按照要求填写即可。<br style=\"outline:0px;\" /></p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\"><span class=\"img_desc\" style=\"outline:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto;text-align:center;\"><img itemprop=\"image\" src=\"http://p.zdmimg.com/201410/10/5437bedd6e189.png_v6.jpg\" _size=\"25198\" alt=\"SHOPBOP 设置个人信息\" style=\"outline:0px;border:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto 10px;max-width:600px;clear:both;\" />SHOPBOP 设置个人信息</span></p><h2 style=\"outline:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;font-size:18px;font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;;color:#333333;line-height:26px;\">二.完善个人信息</h2><h3 style=\"outline:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;;color:#333333;line-height:26px;\">1.设置收货地址<br style=\"outline:0px;\" /></h3><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\">①点击右上角“<strong style=\"outline:0px;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;color:#bb0200;\">Hello ***</span></strong>”用户名，即可进入<strong style=\"outline:0px;\">个人账户</strong>页面。<br style=\"outline:0px;\" /></p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\"><span class=\"img_desc\" style=\"outline:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto;text-align:center;\"><img itemprop=\"image\" src=\"http://p.zdmimg.com/201410/10/5437bedeae698.png_v6.jpg\" _size=\"2537\" alt=\"进入 SHOPBOP 个人账户\" style=\"outline:0px;border:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto 10px;max-width:600px;clear:both;\" />进入 SHOPBOP 个人账户</span></p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\">②个人账户页面包括<strong style=\"outline:0px;\">账户信息、首选项、订单记录、礼券</strong>以及推荐朋友几个功能选择。</p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\"><span class=\"img_desc\" style=\"outline:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto;text-align:center;\"><img itemprop=\"image\" src=\"http://p.zdmimg.com/201410/10/5437bedf3c655.png_v6.jpg\" _size=\"4215\" alt=\"个人账户页面\" style=\"outline:0px;border:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto 10px;max-width:600px;clear:both;\" />个人账户页面</span></p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\"><span class=\"img_desc\" style=\"outline:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto;text-align:center;\"><img itemprop=\"image\" src=\"http://p.zdmimg.com/201410/10/5437bee02843b.png_v6.jpg\" _size=\"4547\" alt=\"个人账户页面2\" style=\"outline:0px;border:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto 10px;max-width:600px;clear:both;\" />个人账户页面2</span></p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\">③选择“账户信息”中的“<strong style=\"outline:0px;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;color:#bb0200;\">通讯录</span></strong>”，点击“<strong style=\"outline:0px;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;color:#bb0200;\">添加新地址</span></strong>”，进入填写地址页面。</p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\"><span class=\"img_desc\" style=\"outline:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto;text-align:center;\"><img itemprop=\"image\" src=\"http://p.zdmimg.com/201410/10/5437bee0dfdd1.png_v6.jpg\" _size=\"3350\" alt=\"添加新收获地址\" style=\"outline:0px;border:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto 10px;max-width:600px;clear:both;\" />添加新收获地址</span></p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\">④需要注意的是，虽然网站贴心地提供了中文页面，但地址的填写仍旧只支持<strong style=\"outline:0px;\">英文或拼音</strong>输入（中文符号也不支持）。寄往国内地址的话，小编<strong style=\"outline:0px;\">建议大家都填写拼音地址，并且按照中文语序填写即可</strong>。例如，<strong style=\"outline:0px;\">北京市朝阳区值得买路月光小区88号</strong>，则填写<strong style=\"outline:0px;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;color:#bb0200;\">BeiJingShi，ChaoYangQu，ZhiDeMai Lu，YueGuang XiaoQu，88 hao</span></strong> 即可。 </p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\">以我们海淘直邮的经验，电话号码经常会在包裹单上消失，建议<strong style=\"outline:0px;\">在地址栏里填写电话号码</strong>，方便派件员联系。填写完毕，点击“<strong style=\"outline:0px;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;color:#bb0200;\">保存</span></strong>”即可。</p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\"><span class=\"img_desc\" style=\"outline:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto;text-align:center;\"><img itemprop=\"image\" src=\"http://p.zdmimg.com/201410/10/5437bee160e9a.png_v6.jpg\" _size=\"8340\" alt=\"填写收货地址\" style=\"outline:0px;border:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto 10px;max-width:600px;clear:both;\" />填写收货地址</span></p><h3 style=\"outline:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;;color:#333333;line-height:26px;\">2.选择默认运送方式</h3><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\">选择“<strong style=\"outline:0px;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;color:#bb0200;\">首选项</span></strong>”里的“<strong style=\"outline:0px;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;color:#bb0200;\">优选运送方式</span></strong>”，SHOPBOP网目前提供三种运送方式，选项中的命名比较类似，不好分辨，以下三张图示，按顺序对应即可；包括<strong style=\"outline:0px;\">Shopbop Global</strong>、<strong style=\"outline:0px;\">DHL/UPS 国际快递</strong>以及<strong style=\"outline:0px;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;color:#bb0200;\">USPS国际邮政</span></strong>，优缺点对比如下方表格，大家按需选择即可。<br style=\"outline:0px;\" /></p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\"><span class=\"img_desc\" style=\"outline:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto;text-align:center;\"><img itemprop=\"image\" src=\"http://p.zdmimg.com/201410/10/5437bee1e25ca.png_v6.jpg\" _size=\"16558\" alt=\"选择送货方式\" style=\"outline:0px;border:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto 10px;max-width:600px;clear:both;\" />选择送货方式</span></p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\"><span class=\"img_desc\" style=\"outline:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto;text-align:center;\"><img itemprop=\"image\" src=\"http://p.zdmimg.com/201410/10/5437bee27375a.png_v6.jpg\" _size=\"223401\" alt=\"送货方式对比\" style=\"outline:0px;border:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto 10px;max-width:600px;clear:both;\" />送货方式对比</span></p><h3 style=\"outline:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;;color:#333333;line-height:26px;\">3.填写支付信息</h3><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\">①SHOPBOP网不仅支持双币信用卡，还可使用国内<span style=\"outline:0px;color:#bb0200;\">单币银联卡</span>，但仅支持<span style=\"outline:0px;color:#bb0200;\">62开头</span>的信用卡。<br style=\"outline:0px;\" /></p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\"><span class=\"img_desc\" style=\"outline:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto;text-align:center;\"><img itemprop=\"image\" src=\"http://p.zdmimg.com/201410/10/5437bee7106b0.png_v6.jpg\" _size=\"9186\" alt=\"多种支付方式\" style=\"outline:0px;border:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto 10px;max-width:600px;clear:both;\" />多种支付方式</span></p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\"><span class=\"img_desc\" style=\"outline:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto;text-align:center;\"><img itemprop=\"image\" src=\"http://p.zdmimg.com/201410/10/5437bee80cd70.png_v6.jpg\" _size=\"6196\" alt=\"银联支付\" style=\"outline:0px;border:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto 10px;max-width:600px;clear:both;\" />银联支付</span></p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\">②点击“<strong style=\"outline:0px;\">账户信息</strong>”里的“<strong style=\"outline:0px;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;color:#bb0200;\">信用卡</span></strong>”，再点击“<strong style=\"outline:0px;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;color:#bb0200;\">添加新卡</span></strong>”，进入填写页面。</p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\"><span class=\"img_desc\" style=\"outline:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto;text-align:center;\"><img itemprop=\"image\" src=\"http://p.zdmimg.com/201410/10/5437bee5823d8.png_v6.jpg\" _size=\"1364\" alt=\"添加信用卡\" style=\"outline:0px;border:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto 10px;max-width:600px;clear:both;\" />添加信用卡</span></p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\">③按提示要求填写信用卡信息以及账单地址。账单地址若为之前填写的收货地址，则可直接选择，若否，则选择“<strong style=\"outline:0px;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;color:#bb0200;\">添加新账单地址</span></strong>”，在弹出的下拉页面里填写即可，规则与填写收货地址相同。填写完毕，点击“<strong style=\"outline:0px;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;color:#bb0200;\">保存</span></strong>”即可。</p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\"><span class=\"img_desc\" style=\"outline:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto;text-align:center;\"><img itemprop=\"image\" src=\"http://p.zdmimg.com/201410/10/5437bee87f83e.png_v6.jpg\" _size=\"16376\" alt=\"添加账单地址\" style=\"outline:0px;border:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto 10px;max-width:600px;clear:both;\" />添加账单地址</span></p><h2 style=\"outline:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;font-size:18px;font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;;color:#333333;line-height:26px;\">三.SHOPBOP网购物及支付流程</h2><h3 style=\"outline:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;;color:#333333;line-height:26px;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;font-size:14px;\">1.商品分类</span><br style=\"outline:0px;\" /></h3><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;\">大家可以按照新款上市、品牌分类、精选推荐、折扣促销、造型杂志的主题来挑选，即便不买，来看看最新潮流走向，或是学习下搭配造型都是不错的。或者以服饰、鞋履、包袋、配饰的分类来选购，更加直观；每个分类底下又有更详细的分类，非常贴心。</span><br style=\"outline:0px;\" /></p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\"><span class=\"img_desc\" style=\"outline:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto;text-align:center;\"><img itemprop=\"image\" src=\"http://p.zdmimg.com/201410/10/5437bee92ba89.png_v6.jpg\" _size=\"6018\" alt=\"商品分类\" style=\"outline:0px;border:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto 10px;max-width:600px;clear:both;\" />商品分类</span></p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\"><span class=\"img_desc\" style=\"outline:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto;text-align:center;\"><img itemprop=\"image\" src=\"http://p.zdmimg.com/201410/10/5437bee9bf612.png_v6.jpg\" _size=\"6278\" alt=\"商品分类 2\" style=\"outline:0px;border:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto 10px;max-width:600px;clear:both;\" />商品分类 2</span></p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\">另外SHOPBOP网每天更新的品牌或专场，会在首页的轮播图展示；同时点击左上角“<span style=\"outline:0px;color:#bb0200;\"><strong style=\"outline:0px;\">选购该页造型</strong></span>”，则可快捷购买<strong style=\"outline:0px;\">每个页面的造型搭配</strong>；或者点击右上角“<span style=\"outline:0px;color:#bb0200;\"><strong style=\"outline:0px;\">选购RAG &amp; BONE</strong></span>”，则可进入<strong style=\"outline:0px;\">每日更新专场</strong>。<br style=\"outline:0px;\" /></p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\"><span class=\"img_desc\" style=\"outline:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto;text-align:center;\"><img itemprop=\"image\" src=\"http://p.zdmimg.com/201410/10/5437beea5e40c.png_v6.jpg\" _size=\"603829\" alt=\"SHOPBOP 每日精选专场\" style=\"outline:0px;border:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto 10px;max-width:600px;clear:both;\" />SHOPBOP 每日精选专场</span></p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\"><span class=\"img_desc\" style=\"outline:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto;text-align:center;\"><img itemprop=\"image\" src=\"http://p.zdmimg.com/201410/10/5437beebe60be.png_v6.jpg\" _size=\"63456\" alt=\"设计师搭配建议\" style=\"outline:0px;border:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto 10px;max-width:600px;clear:both;\" />设计师搭配建议</span></p><h3 style=\"outline:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;;color:#333333;line-height:26px;\">2.商品详情页面</h3><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;\">找到我们要购买的商品之后，进入商品详情页面，以这款<a href=\"http://choiceplus.com.cn/ger.php?uid=11jfkg4&amp;url=http%3a%2f%2fcn.shopbop.com%2fpetty-flat-inside-zip-bootie%2fvp%2fv%3d1%2f845524441906729.htm\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"outline:0px;color:#5188a6;text-decoration:none;cursor:pointer;\">Sam Edelman Petty 小山羊皮短靴</a></span><span style=\"outline:0px;\">为例，页面分为三栏。</span></p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;\">第一栏包括商品品名、价格、可选的颜色以及尺码、用户评论等；第二栏则是商品图片；最右侧则是商品介绍，这里需要关注商</span><span style=\"outline:0px;\">品介绍中的<strong style=\"outline:0px;\">尺寸说明</strong>，SHOPBOP网给出的尺码表十分详细，会换算成我国尺码和厘米，方便用户对照，但是一般这个尺码表是通用型，部分品牌尺码不一样，还需格外注意，最好还是参照官方尺码表。</span><br style=\"outline:0px;\" /></p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;\"></span></p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\"><span class=\"img_desc\" style=\"outline:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto;text-align:center;\"><img itemprop=\"image\" src=\"http://p.zdmimg.com/201410/10/5437beec83334.png_v6.jpg\" _size=\"33018\" alt=\"商品规格选择\" style=\"outline:0px;border:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto 10px;max-width:600px;clear:both;\" />商品规格选择</span></p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\"><span class=\"img_desc\" style=\"outline:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto;text-align:center;\"><img itemprop=\"image\" src=\"http://p.zdmimg.com/201410/10/5437beee6d9d0.png_v6.jpg\" _size=\"6748\" alt=\"商品信息栏\" style=\"outline:0px;border:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto 10px;max-width:600px;clear:both;\" />商品信息栏</span></p><h3 style=\"outline:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;;color:#333333;line-height:26px;\">3.购买及使用优惠码</h3><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\">①选择好商品配色、尺码等规格后，点击页面右侧中间的“<strong style=\"outline:0px;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;color:#bb0200;\">添加至购物车</span></strong>”按钮即可将商品加入购物车了。<span style=\"outline:0px;\">加入购物车后可以选择继续购物或者立即结算。也可点击右上角的“<strong style=\"outline:0px;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;color:#bb0200;\">购物车</span></strong>”进入购物车页面。在购物车页面我们可以查看订单总计金额，并且在页面左侧此输入<strong style=\"outline:0px;\">优惠码</strong>，输入完毕需要点击“<strong style=\"outline:0px;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;color:#bb0200;\">应用代码</span></strong>”才能让优惠码生效。需要注意，<strong style=\"outline:0px;\">这里只能输入优惠码，而不能使用购物礼券哦</strong>。</span></p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\"><span class=\"img_desc\" style=\"outline:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto;text-align:center;\"><img itemprop=\"image\" src=\"http://p.zdmimg.com/201410/10/5437beeef2a91.jpg_v6.jpg\" _size=\"99861\" alt=\"添加优惠码\" style=\"outline:0px;border:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto 10px;max-width:600px;clear:both;\" />添加优惠码</span></p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\">②确认金额之后，即可点击页面右侧的“<strong style=\"outline:0px;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;color:#bb0200;\">付款</span></strong>”按钮，进入结算步骤了。</p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\"><span class=\"img_desc\" style=\"outline:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto;text-align:center;\"><img itemprop=\"image\" src=\"http://p.zdmimg.com/201410/10/5437bef0a1545.jpg_v6.jpg\" _size=\"54766\" alt=\"订单金额信息\" style=\"outline:0px;border:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto 10px;max-width:600px;clear:both;\" />订单金额信息</span></p><h3 style=\"outline:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;;color:#333333;line-height:26px;\">4.支付</h3><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\">①在结算页面，我们可以点击“<strong style=\"outline:0px;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;color:#bb0200;\">更改</span></strong>”修改送货方式，这里默认选择的是7-20个工作日的USPS国际邮政投递，上面已经对比过了，这里不多赘述。有其他需求的可以在此修改。同时在货运信息一栏还会显示收货地址和支付信息，在此核对即可。</p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\"><span class=\"img_desc\" style=\"outline:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto;text-align:center;\"><img itemprop=\"image\" src=\"http://p.zdmimg.com/201410/10/5437bef120dc2.jpg_v6.jpg\" _size=\"61874\" alt=\"修改送货方式\" style=\"outline:0px;border:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto 10px;max-width:600px;clear:both;\" />修改送货方式</span></p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\">②在页面下方还可以看到<strong style=\"outline:0px;\">Gift Certificates</strong>，这才是SHOPBOP的<strong style=\"outline:0px;\">购物礼券</strong>，而不是折扣码，再次输入礼券号，之后点击下方的“<span style=\"outline:0px;color:#bb0200;\"><strong style=\"outline:0px;\">使用礼券</strong></span>”就可以让它生效，抵扣部分订单金额了。</p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\"><span class=\"img_desc\" style=\"outline:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto;text-align:center;\"><img itemprop=\"image\" src=\"http://p.zdmimg.com/201410/10/5437bef19491f.jpg_v6.jpg\" _size=\"86366\" alt=\"使用SHOPBOP礼券\" style=\"outline:0px;border:0px;display:block;margin:0px auto 10px;max-width:600px;clear:both;\" />使用SHOPBOP礼券</span></p><p itemprop=\"description\" style=\"outline:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;line-height:26px;word-break:break-all;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:arial;font-size:14px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:26px;\">③确认完订单信息之后，点击页面右下角的“<strong style=\"outline:0px;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;color:#bb0200;\">下订单</span></strong>”就完成支付过程，确认订单了，之后SHOPBOP会向你的注册邮箱发送订单确认邮件，确认之后就是坐等收货的时间啦。</p><p itemprop=\"description